OL,3,CGrandmother scoops #1 million for
OL,4,Cfamily playing late husband's lottery
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,F"I don't even know what all the
OL,8,Fnumbers meant to Derek but whatever
OL,9,Fthey represent, they have turned out
OL,10,Fto be very lucky for us.
OL,12,F"It honestly feels like he's still
OL,13,Flooking out for us.
OL,15,F"I know he'd be over the moon."
OL,17,FMrs Tresadern was at home alone when
OL,18,Fshe discovered the win and immediately
OL,19,Fcalled her son.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUwD@_O]
