OL,3,CGrandmother scoops #1 million for
OL,4,Cfamily playing late husband's lottery
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,F"With my mobility issues, I need
OL,8,Fsomewhere to live that's easier to
OL,9,Fmanage," she said.
OL,11,F"Now I'll have comfort, independence
OL,12,Fand peace of mind.
OL,14,F"It's such a relief."
OL,16,FShe continued: "I want to buy a new
OL,17,Fengagement ring.
OL,19,F"Derek bought me a second ring years
OL,20,Fafter our original one wore out, but
OL,21,Fthat's become damaged too.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@HO]sD@AOUvD@AOUvD@UO]xD@POU{D@
