OL,3,CGrandmother scoops #1 million for
OL,4,Cfamily playing late husband's lottery
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,FKathy Garrett, senior winners' adviser
OL,8,Fat Allwyn, operator of The National
OL,9,FLottery, said: "Hugecongratulations
OL,10,Fto Rose, Barry and Julie on this
OL,11,Fincredible win.
OL,13,F"There's something truly special about
OL,14,Fthe fact Derek chose the winning
OL,15,Fnumbers many years ago and that the
OL,16,Ffamily continued playing them to
OL,17,Fhonour him."
OL,19,FThe trio won #1 million on April 18
OL,20,Fafter matching five main numbers and
OL,21,Fone bonus ball on the Lotto draw.
OL,26,@qD@POUuD@AOUyD@LO]
